# 1. Force Unix line endings for all source code
# This prevents "Invalid Character" errors in compilers/assemblers
* text=auto eol=lf

# 2. C and Header files: use C-specific diffing logic
*.c diff=cpp
*.h diff=cpp

# 3. Assembly files: ensure they are treated as text
*.s text
*.S text
*.asm text

# 4. Linker scripts and Makefiles
*.ld text
Makefile text
Kbuild text

# 5. Binary files: PROTECT THESE
# This prevents Git from trying to "fix" line endings in data, which would corrupt them
*.bin binary
*.img binary
*.iso binary
*.o   binary
*.a   binary

# 6. Documentation
*.md text